From Booties to Boots

Rightfully so, when countless consumers think “Eastbay” and “footwear,” their first thought is athletic and casual kicks – after all, we are the go-to, online source for avid sneakerheads everywhere. But our website also offers hundreds of leading brand-name boots for men, women, and kids of all ages. For casual strolling, light hiking, or serious tromping in any terrain and any weather, you’ll find great-looking, ruggedly constructed models that offer outstanding comfort and support.  

Hit the trail with the unmistakable woodsman look of the Timberline 6″ Premium Waterproof Boot with durable, genuine leather or nubuck upper and Gripstick rubber lugged outsole for sure-footedness on radically uneven surfaces. The Nike Manoa has the appearance of a traditional hiking boot along with a seamless Swoosh symbol that says this trail-ready hiker is equally at home in the city. The classic women’s UGG Neumel suede chukka is wool-lined for warmth and comfort. The North Face Snowfuse lightweight boot is waterproof and insulated to ensure you will stay warm and dry when winter is in full force. 

Be sure to also shop Eastbay for active apparel, including jackets, hoodies, crews, and much more. As a member of the Eastbay FLX Program, you can qualify for free shipping in the lower 48 states and other benefits. We guarantee correct fit, with free return shipping if you need it. Questions? Personal help is available 24/7 both online and by phone.
